  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Phase II: Capturing the Gains: Economic and Social UPGRADING, GLOBAL Production Networks and Trade</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">a)	to understand the opportunities &amp; challenges for promoting economic upgrading (innovation and improved productivity) &amp; social upgrading (employment that meets labour standards and provides decent work) in Global Production networks and trade, &amp; how they may be affected by restructuring following the global crisisb)	to inform more effective strategies &amp; interventions by private companies, governments, civil society organisations, donors, multi-lateral &amp; trade organisations that support economic &amp; social upgrading in GPNs in developing countries.</narrative>
  </description>
